{"tid":296122,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"欠債還錢，難過登天","createTime":"2017-06-24T10:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T15:30:20.000Z","uid":45558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"901fed5cadeb0c87e0129b5505eea2ac420d6532","tid":296122,"uid":45558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:27:05.000Z","msg":"細佬我唔生性，心軟借左錢比個同行前輩。總數四萬蚊。當中還左八千蚊。但佢依家不停拖住我唔還錢比我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為當時年少無知，以為真係信字行頭。咩借據都冇簽，連利息都冇話要收。<br />\n已經遲左兩個月，想請問下有冇咩方法可以逼到佢還比我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知佢住邊，知佢全名。whatsapp 有追佢還錢既記錄，但佢多數打電話黎回覆我。"},{"pid":"88e113151922b23f4b7b0b424c495a0da8b33608","tid":296122,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:33:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19ae7bdb43a4c6b5eb544f99bac4cdfe1052d0f9","tid":296122,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:34:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1be2676aef6ca5f797952b6f4c00d78ca303eae5","tid":296122,"uid":45558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港有小額錢債審裁處呢個平民法庭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但冇簽借據得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79bc29fb08be3c7a2537ed518da63b7ef53ef2c","tid":296122,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:39:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2b063cfdd4836362d1710bfa349ab9c7fbd8f26","tid":296122,"uid":123712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:50:05.000Z","msg":"搵收數公司，但要比佣金"},{"pid":"ad12c21fdef6085cf0382b27199964357d6d0545","tid":296122,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:00:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid"